\u268\'0co sa t\u253\'fdka spracovate\u318\'3esk\u253\'fdch odvetv\u237\'ed, je ot\u225\'e1zne najm\u228\'e4 spracovanie kalamity. Ja si mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee nie je mo\u382\'7en\u233\'e9 st\u225\'e1le sa skr\u253\'fdva\u357\'65 za to, \u382\'7ee je tento probl\u233\'e9m nerie\u353\'61ite\u318\'3en\u253\'fd. Aj v minul\u253\'fdch rokoch najprv bola kalamita Osrblie, teraz bola v listnat\u253\'fdch lesoch, ale to spracovanie bez v\u228\'e4zby na drevospracuj\u250\'faci priemysel asi nebude rie\u353\'61ite\u318\'3en\u233\'e9 na vyu\u382\'7eitie aj t\u253\'fdchto zdrojov.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

